title: 162. Made In America Ft. Christian Walker
itunes:title: 162. Made In America Ft. Christian Walker
description: It's time to bring back common sense to our society. In today's episode, Andy and the crew are joined by Christian Walker. They discuss how standing your ground silences the haters, school systems indoctrinating our kids with their narrative, and the reasoning behind all the division happening in America.
